{"tid":2385923,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部趙立堅：英方試圖把大批港人變成二等英國公民，中方表示強烈憤慨並保留採取進一步措施的權利","createTime":"2021-01-29T09:29:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T12:57:11.000Z","uid":350584,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"9cd024004deb5d5015468181a4faa0dc8e1c3535","tid":2385923,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T09:29:05.000Z","msg":"英國政府將於星期日起實施英國國民海外護照BNO簽證政策，合資格人士當日開始可以在網上登記，預約到位於北角的簽證申請中心，提供指紋及照片，辦理相關手續，2月23日開始，可以透過手機程式提出申請。在北京，外交部表示，中方星期日起不再承認BNO作為旅行證件和身份證明，並保留採取進一步措施的權利。發言人趙立堅說，英方試圖把大批港人變成二等英國公民，已經徹底改變原來中英諒解的BNO性質，嚴重侵犯中國主權，粗暴干涉香港事務和中國內政，嚴重違反國際法和國際關係基本準則，中方表示強烈憤慨，堅決反對。<br />\n<br />\nFrom: RTHK"},{"pid":"6fc2f8258acccc78f5b7f5c27ff69c79594dbc54","tid":2385923,"uid":389613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T09:29:46.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">香港人用 BNO 係搬石頭砸中共春袋</span><br />\n<br />\n原來用 BNO 離開係 Trump 一早 set 左比中共既計時炸彈！我地更應該繼承 Trump 既精神，用 BNO 逼 Biden 同中共開戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"red\">只要有大批香港人離開，會造成現時已經虛弱既經濟徹底崩潰，而中共強行鎖國則引來百國聯軍。</span><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本１：支共反制 BNO 會引致戰爭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n[武俠小說] 因為 BNO 香港變成外交博奕戰場！Trump 偷偷地幫香港插左支定海神針迫 Biden 打柒中共！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2377934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2377934</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本２：支共比 BNO 走引致經濟崩潰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n[神話故事] 中共經濟末日狂奔，BNO 就係大衛與歌利亞決戰粒石頭。港人出走成就 Trump 滅共偉業。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2380593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2380593</a><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n不論你係撐 Trump 既手足、定係支持滅共既手足，今次 BNO Visa 係時候身體力行，用你對腳投票去支持 Trump 呢條滅共戰線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"red\">多你一個好多，少你一個唔掂！你既決定將會成為世界走向正義定係腐敗既關鍵因素！</span>"},{"pid":"394bd9b543edfd2ebf5d898a0da1b5866018e4a5","tid":2385923,"uid":350584,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T09:31:21.000Z","msg":"外交部好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1422e357932f1ea19673491933f1c6e3259183c","tid":2385923,"uid":389613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"394bd9b543edfd2ebf5d898a0da1b5866018e4a5","tid":2385923,"uid":350584,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T09:31:21.000Z","msg":"外交部好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T09:32:07.000Z","msg":"怕撚咩，香港人預左攬炒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17fb51f92419705e7647b2fcb5e2fe788324147e","tid":2385923,"uid":54093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T09:33:36.000Z","msg":"做二等支那公民同二等英國公民真係好難抉擇 。。"},{"pid":"2b6734d8f5553cb8659c98824d0f2b98fc4eaa8a","tid":2385923,"uid":156652,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T09:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kMjV37t.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkMjV37t.gif&h=b6c8e8c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BwqaS0P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBwqaS0P.gif&h=5cbdf62c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10a025dfc81fc460968626813016b643de213788","tid":2385923,"uid":350584,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2b6734d8f5553cb8659c98824d0f2b98fc4eaa8a","tid":2385923,"uid":156652,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T09:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kMjV37t.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkMjV37t.gif&h=b6c8e8c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BwqaS0P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBwqaS0P.gif&h=5cbdf62c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T09:35:00.000Z","ms